{"tid":1343324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係有 primary source 之前，應該假定白衫未死，就算死都唔係「飛天南」！或者根本冇一個黑社會叫「飛天南」！","createTime":"2019-07-21T18:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T20:49:20.000Z","uid":42250,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ae31e02037abd84812fcab219cffb7df3cfb5612","tid":1343324,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:34:32.000Z","msg":"呢個唯一一個話有叔父死左既來源，只係一張 whatsapp cap 圖，仲係 forward 過唔知幾多次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁樣同 928 話有傳12點唔走黑警就會見人就射有咩分別？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SpYrTUV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSpYrTUV.png&h=d5527de1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個來源鳩UP唔洗本，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分分鐘冇一個黑社會叫做飛天南</span></span></strong><br />\n直頭係傳移視線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢一邊廂，有條女之前facebook 話幫頭先白衫搵腰包<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q9dGH0O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ9dGH0O.png&h=950d7d36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VOV59pq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVOV59pq.png&h=e3d39be8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且呢個人話白衫仲未死<br />\n<br />\n睇曬兩邊，根本由頭到尾大家得到既資料只係有隻白衫暈左，搓完CPR 電完都冇反應上車<br />\n死左未？唔知<br />\n係唔係叫飛天南？唔知<br />\n有冇飛天南呢個黑社會？唔知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但如果呢個人根本未死，即係所有關於飛天南既資料都好大機會係鳩UP</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d22060cb12098fc4aebb3943b40cdea195d0bd88","tid":1343324,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:35:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有片 黑社會夾道歡迎何君堯</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/82ejs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F82ejs&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcv%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=1622588b\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/82ejs</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/nMyb41y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnMyb41y.gif&h=7f895d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">元朗黑社會瘋狂抽打路人</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/b0itt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fb0itt&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcv%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=8d3a9d01\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/b0itt</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/fVN8nNU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfVN8nNU.gif&h=ca4b6db9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n紅的一早收哂風，路德圍泊滿的士</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/uox17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fuox17&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcv%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=c8e76b73\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/uox17</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/73vaBmz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F73vaBmz.png&h=a84129d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">阿sir表示無時間睇錶</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wusiuwu/videos/10162072219475035/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwusiuwu%2Fvideos%2F10162072219475035%2F&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcv%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=613d0e70\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wusiuwu/videos/10162072219475035/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n柳俊江被毆致重傷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kxhDKKb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkxhDKKb.jpg&h=96301925&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc43437985c7e7a95640d8ff07d1b63b29071ddd","tid":1343324,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score